@startuml secuencia_filmrecord
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam SequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #3B82F6
skinparam ActorBorderColor #555555

title GestorCOC - Flujo Completo de Registro Filmico y Verificacion CREV

actor "Operador Basico\n(OP_EXTRACTION)" as Op
actor "Administrador\n(ADMIN)" as Crev
participant "Angular SPA\n/records" as SPA
participant "FilmRecordViewSet\nDRF" as API
participant "IntegrityService\nrecords/services.py" as Service
participant "FilmRecord\nModel" as Model
database "Base de datos" as DB

== 1. Crear Registro Filmico ==

Op -> SPA : Completa formulario\n(causa, camara, operador,\nrango horario)
SPA -> API : POST /api/film-records/\n{ camera, operator, judicial_case_number,\n  start_time, end_time, ... }
API -> Model : FilmRecord.objects.create(...)
Model -> DB : INSERT filmrecord
DB --> Model : id=42
Model --> API : FilmRecord(id=42,\ndelivery_status=PENDIENTE,\nis_editable=True)
API --> SPA : HTTP 201 Created\n{ id: 42, delivery_status: "PENDIENTE" }
SPA --> Op : Registro creado #42

== 2. Registrar Backup y Hash ==

Op -> SPA : Edita registro #42\n(backup_path, file_hash,\nhash_algorithm=sha256)
SPA -> API : PATCH /api/film-records/42/\n{ has_backup: true,\n  backup_path: "/storage/...",\n  file_hash: "abc123...",\n  hash_algorithm: "sha256" }
API -> Model : filmrecord.save()
Model -> DB : UPDATE filmrecord SET has_backup=True, file_hash=...
DB --> Model : OK
API --> SPA : HTTP 200 OK
SPA --> Op : Backup registrado

note over Op, DB : El operador puede usar /integrity\npara calcular el hash localmente\nantes de ingresarlo aqui

== 3. Verificacion CREV ==

Crev -> SPA : Accede a registros pendientes\nde verificacion
SPA -> API : POST /api/film-records/42/verify_by_crev/\n{ verified_by_crev_id: <person_id> }
API -> API : Valida role == ADMIN
API -> Model : filmrecord.verified_by_crev = person\nfilmrecord.verification_date = now()
note right of Model : save() automaticamente\nsetea is_editable = False
Model -> DB : UPDATE filmrecord SET\nverified_by_crev_id=5,\nverification_date=NOW(),\nis_editable=False
DB --> Model : OK
API --> SPA : HTTP 200 OK\n{ is_editable: false,\n  verification_date: "2026-03-06T..." }
SPA --> Crev : Registro verificado y bloqueado

== 4. Descargar Certificado PDF ==

Crev -> SPA : Solicita certificado
SPA -> API : GET /api/film-records/42/verification_certificate/
API -> Service : generar_pdf_certificado(filmrecord)
Service --> API : PDF bytes
API --> SPA : HTTP 200\nContent-Type: application/pdf
SPA --> Crev : Descarga certificado.pdf

@enduml
